Package: csdr
Title: Causal Sufficient Dimension Reduction
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Thomas", "Hsiao", 
    email = "thomas.hsiao@emory.edu", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-7848-7992"))
Description: Implements methods for causal sufficient dimension reduction with 
    multiple continuous exposures. The package estimates low-dimensional
    exposure summaries that preserve the causal exposure-response surface, with
    tools for estimating the causal central mean subspace, selecting the
    structural dimension, computing subspace importance scores, and estimating
    the reduced exposure-response surface. 
